==English==

===Etymology===
[[feed] + corruption of [[cog]].

===Noun===
'''[[feed]] [[dog]]'''

# On a [[sewing machine]], the toothed [[mechanism]] that uses a forward, down, back, and up motion against the [[presser foot]] to advance the fabric through the machine evenly.  See also [[w:sewing_machine]].

